his life to save yours.

40:24.596 --> 40:29.731
And I know that he'd be so proud
of the man you are today.

40:29.775 --> 40:31.733
The Ghost told me

40:31.777 --> 40:33.474
he left another bomb
out there somewhere.

40:33.518 --> 40:34.649
One he built just for me.

40:34.693 --> 40:36.477
One I'm supposed
to find someday,

40:36.521 --> 40:37.739
and I'm pretty sure
it's meant to kill me
or someone I care about.

40:37.783 --> 40:40.699
Mac, he said that
to get inside your head.

40:40.742 --> 40:43.266
But you can't be obsessed
with him anymore.

40:43.310 --> 40:45.486
You see where obsession
led Eileen.

40:47.619 --> 40:49.577
The Ghost is gone.

40:49.621 --> 40:51.753
Don't let him haunt you.

40:51.797 --> 40:54.539
BOZER:
Hey, Mac, come here.

40:54.582 --> 40:58.760
Jack's calling from a bar in
Brazil, and he's got stories.

